(20, 'Ross.Malonda@qbe.com', 'Ross Mark Malonda', 'Oil Shortage - Query - OG', '<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"Microsoft Word 15 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]><style>v\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style><![endif]--><style><!--\n/* Font Definitions */\n@font-face\n	{font-family:\"Cambria Math\";\n	panose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4;}\n@font-face\n	{font-family:Calibri;\n	panose-1:2 15 5 2 2 2 4 3 2 4;}\n@font-face\n	{font-family:Aptos;}\n@font-face\n	{font-family:\"QBE Sans\";\n	panose-1:2 11 5 3 2 2 3 2 2 4;}\n@font-face\n	{font-family:\"QBE Sans Medium\";\n	panose-1:2 11 6 3 2 2 3 2 2 4;}\n/* Style Definitions */\np.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n	{margin:0cm;\n	font-size:12.0pt;\n	font-family:\"Aptos\",sans-serif;\n	mso-ligatures:standardcontextual;\n	mso-fareast-language:EN-US;}\nspan.EmailStyle17\n	{mso-style-type:personal-compose;\n	font-family:\"Aptos\",sans-serif;\n	color:windowtext;}\n.MsoChpDefault\n	{mso-style-type:export-only;\n	mso-fareast-language:EN-US;}\n@page WordSection1\n	{size:612.0pt 792.0pt;\n	margin:72.0pt 72.0pt 72.0pt 72.0pt;}\ndiv.WordSection1\n	{page:WordSection1;}\n/* List Definitions */\n@list l0\n	{mso-list-id:1307972900;\n	mso-list-template-ids:-1956087278;}\nol\n	{margin-bottom:0cm;}\nul\n	{margin-bottom:0cm;}\n--></style>\n</head>\n<body lang=\"EN-PH\" link=\"#467886\" vlink=\"#96607D\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word\">\n<div class=\"WordSection1\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Hi Team Launchpad,<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Good day.<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">May we please request your assistance in securing confirmation and updates from the building admin regarding the following:<o:p></o:p></p>\n<ol style=\"margin-top:0cm\" start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><b>What preparations are currently in place in the building for the potential fuel shortage?</b><o:p></o:p></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><b>What is the present status or condition of your fuel supply?</b><o:p></o:p></li><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><b>Do you have an existing agreement with a fuel provider, and what assurances or commitments have they provided regarding supply availability?</b><o:p></o:p></li></ol>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Thank you, and we look forward to your response.<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Regards,<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<div>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:24.2pt\">\n<td width=\"328\" style=\"width:246.05pt;border:none;border-top:solid #F9760A 3.0pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:24.2pt\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:105%\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans Medium&quot;,sans-serif;color:#0076BC;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">Ross Mark Malonda</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:14.15pt\">\n<td width=\"328\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:246.05pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.15pt\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:105%\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans Medium&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">Facilities Manager&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:14.15pt\">\n<td width=\"328\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:246.05pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.15pt\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:105%\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">Facilities and Administration\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans&quot;,sans-serif;color:#F9760A;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">&nbsp;<b>|</b></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">&nbsp;\n Group Shared Services Centre</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:14.15pt\">\n<td width=\"328\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:246.05pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.15pt\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:1.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:105%\">\n<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">+63 917 110 4498&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans&quot;,sans-serif;color:#F9760A;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">&nbsp;<b>|</b></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&quot;QBE Sans&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-PH\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line