lt:auto\">Hi Sir Ross,<o:p></o:p></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>The purpose of this request is for employee headcount monitoring by the building administration.&nbsp;This information will be used for emergency preparedness. In case of emergencies such as earthquakes or fire incidents, the building management needs to be aware\n of the headcount in each office and identify individuals who may require priority assistance during evacuation.<o:p></o:p></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Regards,</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n<div>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:69.75pt\">\n<td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt;height:69.75pt;overflow:hidden\">\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;padding:0cm\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\" style=\"width:1.2986in;height:1.2986in\" id=\"m_-2103891951424920435m_-502379286742238796Picture_x0020_1\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"Image removed by sender.\"></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt 5.0pt;height:69.75pt;overflow:hidden\">\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Team Launchpad</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Receptionist/ Administrative Staff</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#222222\">admin</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><a href=\"mailto:hello@launchpadcoworkingph.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1155CC\">@launchpadcoworkingph.com</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:blue\">Commercenter:\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">+63 287763321 | +63 9563958065</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:blue\">One Griffinstone:\n</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">+63 288479850 | +63 9</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#222222\">611437836</span><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><a href=\"https://www.launchpadcoworkingph.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1155CC\">Launchpad Coworking</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">\n | </span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/launchpadcoworkingph/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1155CC\">Instagram</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">\n | </span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LaunchpadCoworkingPH\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1155CC\">Facebook</span></a></span><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><i><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#222222\">Launchpad Coworking</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm\"><i><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#222222\">... Where ideas fly.</span></i><o:p></o:p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto\">On Wed, Mar 11, 2026 at 4:04<span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> </span>PM Ross Mark Malonda &lt;<a href=\"mailto:Ross.Malonda@qbe.com\" target=\"_blank\">Ross.Malonda@qbe.com</a>&gt;\n wrote:<o:p></o:p></p>\n</div>\n<blockquote style=\"border:none;border-left:solid #CCCCCC 1.0pt;padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 6.0pt;margin-left:4.8pt;margin-top:5.', '<CY4PR0201MB3571B76CE6D399B8E3B9A4E79456A@CY4PR0201MB3571.namprd02.prod.outlook.com>', '[{\"filename\":\"image001.png\",\"url\":\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1e2wWPCXhGnY-jN0YPYr8oTwhZVWLuuSb/view?usp=drivesdk\",\"type\":\"image/png\"},{\"filename\":\"image002.jpg\",\"url\":\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iaZX7LlZ3fB5pDxSSWjUDlJ35JsxJEaL/view?usp=drivesdk\",\"type\":\"image/jpeg\"}]', '2026-03-26 04:22:48', NULL);
