(33, 'kath@launchpadcoworkingph.com', 'Kath Delos Reyes', 'Re: Inquiry on Contingency Plans Amid Potential Power and Fuel Shortages', '<div dir=\"ltr\"><div><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\">Hi Ms. Jergen,</font></div><div><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\"><br></font></div><div><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\">Thank you for your response.</font></div><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\"><br>May I ask if you could share where the other tenants are sourcing or renting their standby generators? This would help us explore similar arrangements on our end.</font><div><br><div><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_signature\" data-smartmail=\"gmail_signature\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\"><div style=\"margin-left:0pt\" align=\"left\">Regards,</div><div style=\"margin-left:0pt\" align=\"left\"><span><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:0pt\" align=\"left\"><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse\"><colgroup><col width=\"139\"><col width=\"314\"></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height:69.75pt\"><td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);background-color:transparent;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:125px;height:125px\"><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/0XC-wQTNTk2tUfKJtALgCrgryAoLCblNCiFbRVCoAU2n0AH7kDJMHmxfZxf9qB5xPDFx3M18xH_wXSGw_sZgkw43-2udhvmAhNlSrPLKZB49m2wfYJmeG7iojBTEQF1KKrHJ2zn6\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\"></span></span></p></td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Kath Delos Reyes</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);background-color:transparent;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Office Manager</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"mailto:kath@launchpadcoworkingph.com\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);background-color:transparent;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">kath@launchpadcoworkingph.com</span></a></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">+63 920 956 6904</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://www.launchpadcoworkingph.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Launchpad Coworking</span></a><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"> | </span><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/launchpadcoworkingph/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Instagram</span></a><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"> | </span><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LaunchpadCoworkingPH\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Facebook</span></a></p><br><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(34,34,34);font-style:italic;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">Launchpad Coworking</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(34,34,34);font-style:italic;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">... Where ideas fly.</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></span></div></font></span></div></div></div><br></div></div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote gmail_quote_container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Fri, Mar 27, 2026 at 10:40 AM Jergen Almazan &lt;<a href=\"mailto:jalmazan@paec.com.ph\">jalmazan@paec.com.ph</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px 0.8ex;border-left:1px solid rgb(204,204,204);padding-left:1ex\"><div class=\"msg-6783902747799842392\">\n\n\n\n\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nHello Ms. Kath,</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nHappy Friday!</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nApologies for the delay of response with regards on your queries.</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nFor Bldg. 2, we have 20-ampere supply for each tenant however for Bldg. 1 we don&#39;t have. Our Genset unit is used solely for emergency power backup during utility outages to maintain safe and efficient operations for common areas only (hallways, fire exits,\n emergency lighting, common area safety features).</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nSome of our tenants plans renting a standby generator during power interruptions to avoid further project delays and potential safety risks.</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Aptos,Aptos_EmbeddedFont,Aptos_MSFontService,Calibri,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div id=\"m_1772236584803438302Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_1772236584803438302x_x_x_x_Signature\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);margin:0px\">\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:12pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(34,34,34)\"><b>Regards,</b></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:12pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(34,34,34)\"><b>Jergen Almazan</b><br>\nLeasing &amp; Operations Supervisor</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:black\"><b>Philippine Allied Enterprises Corporation\n</b>(ISO 9001 and 14001 Certified Company)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:black\">2262 Chino Roces Avenue Extension Makati City, Philippines</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:black\">+63(2) 8887-0956</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(17,85,204)\"><a href=\"http://www.bridgestonetires.com.ph/\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWA1ad15bba-80f8-d369-4967-85ce6ee15a7e\" title=\"http://www.bridgestonetires.com.ph/\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);margin:0px\" target=\"_blank\">www.bridgestonetires.com.ph</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:blue;background-color:white\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BridgestonePhilippines\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWAd5a675f6-bdef-2e37-0f7b-4c10d8db432f\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/BridgestonePhilippines\" style=\"color:blue;margin:0px\" target=\"_blank\"><img id=\"m_1772236584803438302x_x_x_x_x_x_x_m_-4709674264438746310x_x_x_x_image_0\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" style=\"width: 0.3854in; height: 0.3854in; max-width: 781px; min-width: auto; min-height: auto; margin: 0px;\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"></a><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bridgestoneph/?hl=en\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWA0fbbae32-8e53-f3e4-a9fe-415166b1d70d\" title=\"https://www.instagram.com/bridgestoneph/?hl=en\" style=\"color:blue;margin:0px\" target=\"_blank\"><img id=\"m_1772236584803438302x_x_x_x_x_x_x_m_-4709674264438746310x_x_x_x_image_2\" width=\"37\" height=\"36\" style=\"width: 0.3958in; height: 0.3854in; max-width: 781px; min-width: auto; min-height: auto; margin: 0px;\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"></a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@BridgestonePH/featured\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWAfe737eda-cbfb-d66c-16c6-66277ca46da0\" title=\"https://www.youtube.com/@BridgestonePH/featured\" style=\"color:blue;margin:0px\" target=\"_blank\"><img id=\"m_1772236584803438302x_x_x_x_x_x_x_m_-4709674264438746310x_x_x_x_image_4\" width=\"36\" height=\"36\" style=\"width: 0.375in; height: 0.375in; max-width: 781px; min-width: auto; min-height: auto; margin: 0px;\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:black\"><img id=\"m_1772236584803438302x_x_x_x_x_x_x_m_-4709674264438746310x_x_x_x_image_3_0\" width=\"174\" height=\"37\" style=\"width: 1.8229in; height: 0.3958in; max-width: 781px; min-width: auto; min-height: auto; margin: 0px;\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:red\"><b><i>CONFIDENTIALITY</i></b></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:0px;background-color:white;margin-top:1em;margin-bottom:1em\">\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:red\"><i>This message is intended only for the person or entity to which it is addressed and may contain information that is privileged, confidential or otherwise protected from disclosure.\n Dissemination, distribution or reproduction of this message or the information contained herein by anyone other than the intended recipient is prohibited and punishable under the law. If you received this message in error, kindly notify us immediately. Thank\n you.</i></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr style=\"display:inline-block;width:98%\">\n<div style=\"font-family:Calibri,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<b>From:</b> Kath Delos Reyes &lt;<a href=\"mailto:kath@launchpadcoworkingph.com\" target=\"_blank\">kath@launchpadcoworkingph.com</a>&gt;<br>\n<b>Sent:</b> Wednesday, March 25, 2026 2:53 PM<br>\n<b>To:</b> Jergen Almazan &lt;<a href=\"mailto:jalmazan@paec.com.ph\" target=\"_blank\">jalmazan@paec.com.ph</a>&gt;<br>\n<b>Cc:</b> Team Launchpad &lt;<a href=\"mailto:admin@launchpadcoworkingph.com\" target=\"_blank\">admin@launchpadcoworkingph.com</a>&gt;; Chelle Tejada &lt;<a href=\"mailto:chelle@launchpadcoworkingph.com\" target=\"_blank\">chelle@launchpadcoworkingph.com</a>&gt;<br>\n<b>Subject:</b> Inquiry on Contingency Plans Amid Potential Power and Fuel Shortages\n</div>\n<div style=\"font-family:Calibri,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12pt;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"direction:ltr;font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nHi Ms. Jergen,</div>\n<div style=\"direction:ltr;font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\n<br>\n</div>\n<div style=\"direction:ltr;font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nI hope you are doing well.<br>\n<br>\nGiven the recent global situation and its potential impact on fuel and energy supply, we would like to inquire about the building’s contingency plans in the event of possible power interruptions or fuel shortages.<br>\n<br>\nWe would appreciate any information you can share regarding:</div>\n<ul style=\"direction:ltr\">\n<li style=\"direction:ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\" role=\"presentation\">Backup power systems and their expected duration of operation</span></li><li style=\"direction:ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\" role=\"presentation\">Fuel supply management for generators</span></li><li style=\"direction:ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\" role=\"presentation\">Priority allocation (if applicable) during extended outages</span></li><li style=\"direction:ltr\"><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\" role=\"presentation\">Any guidelines or protocols tenants should follow during such situations</span></li></ul>\n<div style=\"direction:ltr;font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">\nUnderstanding these measures will help us prepare accordingly and ensure continuity of our operations.<br>\n<br>\nThank you in advance for your assistance. We look forward to your response.</div>\n<div style=\"direction:ltr\"><br>\n</div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"direction:ltr;margin-left:0pt;font-family:arial,sans-serif\">\nRegards,</div>\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left:0pt\">\n<div align=\"left\" style=\"margin-left:0pt\">\n<table style=\"direction:ltr;box-sizing:border-box;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"direction:ltr;padding:5pt;vertical-align:top;width:139px;height:69px\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);line-height:1.2\"><img width=\"125\" height=\"125\" style=\"width: 125px; height: 125px; margin-top: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\" src=\"https://outlook.office.com/mail/id/AAQkAGNlZTYzN2E5LTRjNDktNGZhNC1iZjZkLTJlM2Q1Nzg3YTQzZgAQAAh6YTHkk3JLldH7UBACmlM%3D?nativeVersion=1.2026.317.100\"></span></td>\n<td style=\"direction:ltr;padding:5pt;vertical-align:top;width:314px;height:69px\">\n<p style=\"direction:ltr;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:700\">Kath Delos Reyes</span></p>\n<p style=\"direction:ltr;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Office Manager</span></p>\n<p style=\"direction:ltr;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(17,85,204)\"><a href=\"mailto:kath@launchpadcoworkingph.com\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWAdb145048-4fe1-a701-5253-55ef1fb5a809\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px\" target=\"_blank\">kath@launchpadcoworkingph.com</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"direction:ltr;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\">+63 920 956 6904</span></p>\n<p style=\"direction:ltr;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(17,85,204)\"><a href=\"https://www.launchpadcoworkingph.com/\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWA19dee87e-adb4-d5f7-d17a-bf0dbbcd1a78\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px\" target=\"_blank\">Launchpad\n Coworking</a></span><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\"> |\n</span><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(17,85,204)\"><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/launchpadcoworkingph/\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWA1b52747e-8fab-7a96-88b3-595a9a79c189\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a></span><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\"> |\n</span><span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(17,85,204)\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LaunchpadCoworkingPH\" id=\"m_1772236584803438302OWA6fbf5339-5bcb-a91a-d614-fb0d2d0689cd\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204);margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></span></p>\n<div style=\"direction:ltr;font-family:arial,sans-serif\"><br>\n</div>\n<p style=\"direction:ltr;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(34,34,34)\"><i>Launchpad Coworking</i></span></p>\n<p style=\"direction:ltr;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">\n<span style=\"font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(34,34,34)\"><i>... Where ideas fly.</i></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div></blockquote></div>\n', '<CAJVo9vSv+38U_Ynhyd1wcwC2bFNYbXq6-aEm1K5Pp98ctU+BLA@mail.gmail.com>', '[{\"filename\":\"Outlook-3zhf2udy.png\",\"url\":\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nn2xYmkLfKCVvIX7Ffso-Ry_DSjiHkC3/view?usp=drivesdk\",\"type\":\"image/png\"},{\"filename\":\"Outlook-t3d2utpp.png\",\"url\":\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1D50SbsI7uE6p6VfCDeNpXKfMhjMKtjL2/view?usp=drivesdk\",\"type\":\"image/png\"},{\"filename\":\"Outlook-1g12d1gv.png\",\"url\":\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1orr8sq-YgwKd6Rl0gPAeFm21cS3Hg0tD/view?usp=drivesdk\",\"type\":\"image/png\"},{\"filename\":\"Outlook-33hzjz0c.png\",\"url\":\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mfKvMDOj6hh62wj_5k5L9AIzBsDWcbhv/view?usp=drivesdk\",\"type\":\"image/png\"}]', '2026-03-27 07:35:46', NULL);
