ank you.</font></div></div></div><div><font face=\"tahoma, sans-serif\"><br></font></div><div><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_signature\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\">Regards,<br></font><div><table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse\"><colgroup><col width=\"139\"><col width=\"314\"></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height:69.75pt\"><td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt;overflow:hidden\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);background-color:transparent;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:125px;height:125px\"><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\"><img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/0XC-wQTNTk2tUfKJtALgCrgryAoLCblNCiFbRVCoAU2n0AH7kDJMHmxfZxf9qB5xPDFx3M18xH_wXSGw_sZgkw43-2udhvmAhNlSrPLKZB49m2wfYJmeG7iojBTEQF1KKrHJ2zn6\" width=\"125\" height=\"125\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\"></font></span></span></p></td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt;overflow:hidden\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\">Mae</font></span> <b>Perocho</b></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color:rgb(34,34,34);line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);background-color:transparent;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\">Receptionist/ Administrative Staff</font></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"color:rgb(34,34,34);line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><font face=\"arial, sans-serif\">admin<a href=\"mailto:hello@launchpadcoworkingph.com\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" rel=\"noreferrer noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">@launchpadcoworkingph.com</